summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 226E, Page 16 of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Block 45, H.E. Orr Park Division No. 4 from Duplex Residence Medium Density (RD 7200) to Multiple Residence Low Density (RM 800) Zone and Neighborhood Business (BN) Zone (Petition of R. A. Oliver, C.F. 288621).
